quran[58]{c,v,t}:
  37,145,Ariko twamujugunye ku nkombe ameze nk’umurwayi
  37,146,Maze dutegeka ko (aho yari ari) hamera uruyuzi rwera ibihaza kugira ngo ajye abirya
  37,147,Nuko tumwohereza ku bantu ibihumbi ijana cyangwa banarenga
  37,148,"Maze baremera, nuko tubaha umunezero w’igihe gito"
  37,149,"Ngaho (yewe Muhamadi) babaze uti \"Ese Nyagasani wawe afite abakobwa gusa, hanyuma bo bakagira abahungu"
  37,150,Cyangwa twaremye abamalayika b’abakobwa babireba (ikaba ari yo mpamvu bavuga ko abamalayika ari igitsina gore)
  37,151,"Mu by’ukuri, no mu binyoma byabo (ababangikanyamana b’i Maka) baravuga (bati)"
  37,152,"Allah yarabyaye (bavugaga ko abamalayika ari abakobwa ba Allah)\" Nyamara rwose ni abanyabinyoma"
  37,153,Nonese (ni ukubera iki) yaba yarahisemo abakobwa mu kimbo cy’abahungu
  37,154,Ese mwabaye mute? Amahitamo yanyu ashingira kuki
  37,155,Ese ntimutekereza
  37,156,Cyangwa mufite ibimenyetso bigaragara
  37,157,"Ngaho nimuzane igitabo cyanyu, niba muri abanyakuri"
  37,158,"Kandi banashyize isano hagati ye (Allah) n’amajini, nyamara amajini yo azi neza ko azazanwa (imbere ya Allah kugira ngo acirwe urubanza)"
  37,159,"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamwitirira"
  37,160,Uretse abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera (ni bo batajya bagira ibyo bamwitirira)
  37,161,"Bityo, mu by’ukuri mwe (ababangikanyamana) ndetse n’ibyo musenga bitari Allah"
  37,162,Nta n’umwe (mu bemeramana) mushobora kuyobya
  37,163,Uretse abazajya mu muriro ugurumana
  37,164,Kandi nta n’umwe muri twe (abamalayika) udafite umwanya uzwi (mu ijuru)
  37,165,"Mu by’ukuri, twe (abamalayika) dutonda imirongo (dusenga nk’uko Abayislamu babigenza)"
  37,166,"Kandi mu by’ukuri, ni twe dusingiza (Allah)"
  37,167,"(Kandi mu by’ukuri, ababangikanyamana b’i Maka) bajyaga bavuga bati"
  37,168,Iyo tuza kugira urwibutso nk’urw’abo hambere (mbere y’uko intumwa Muhamadi ihabwa ubutumwa)
  37,169,Mu by’ukuri twari kuba abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera
  37,170,Nyamara (nyuma y’uko Qor’an ibagezeho) barayihakanye kandi vuba aha bazamenya (ukuri)
  37,171,"Kandi rwose, isezerano ryacu ryaje mbere ku bagaragu bacu b’intumwa"
  37,172,"Ko mu by’ukuri, ari bo bazatsinda"
  37,173,"Kandi ko mu by’ukuri, ingabo zacu ari zo zizatsinda"
  37,174,Bityo rero (yewe Muhamadi) birengagizeho igihe gito
  37,175,"Unabahozeho ijisho, kuko bidatinze bazabona (ibihano)"
  37,176,Ese ibihano byacu ni byo bashaka kwihutisha
  37,177,"Bityo, ubwo bizamanukira hafi yabo, kizaba ari igitondo kibi kuri babandi baburiwe"
  37,178,"Bityo, birengagize igihe gito (yewe Muhamadi)"
  37,179,"Unabahozeho ijisho, kuko bidatinze bazabona (ibihano)"
  37,180,"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Nyagasani wawe, Nyagasani Nyiricyubahiro! Ntaho ahuriye n’ibyo bamwitirira"
  37,181,Kandi amahoro nabe ku ntumwa
  37,182,"Kandi ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibya Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  38,1,Swad111! Ndahiriye kuri Qur’an yuje urwibutso
  38,2,Nyamara abahakanye bari mu bwibone n’ubwigomeke
  38,3,"Ese ni ibisekuru bingahe tworetse mbere yabo, bigatakamba by’impitagihe"
  38,4,"(Abarabu b’ababangikanya-mana) batangajwe no kugerwaho n’umuburizi (Muhamadi) ubakomokamo. Nuko abahakanyi baravuga bati \"Uyu ni umurozi w’umubeshyi"
  38,5,"Ese arashaka ko imana (zacu) zose ziba Imana imwe? Mu by’ ukuri, iki ni ikintu gitangaje"
  38,6,"Maze ibikomerezwa muri bo bigenda bivuga biti \"Nimugende munambe ku mana zanyu. Mu by’ukuri, uyu ni umugambi wateguwe"
  38,7,Ibi ntitwigeze tubyumva mu myizerere yo hambere. Ibi nta kindi biri cyo usibye kuba ari ibihimbano
  38,8,"Ese ni we wenyine muri twe waba warahishuriwe urwibutso? Ahubwo barashidikanya ku rwibutso rwanjye (Qur’an), kuko batarasogongera ku bihano byanjye"
  38,9,"Ese baba bafite ibigega by’impuhwe za Nyagasani wawe, Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Ugaba bihebuje"
  38,10,"Cyangwa baba bafite ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo? Niba ari uko bimeze, ngaho nibazamuke mu kirere bakoresheje uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose (maze bakumire ubutumwa)"
  38,11,Izo ni ingabo zizatsindwa (nk’uko) iz’udutsiko zatsinzwe (mbere)
  38,12,"Mbere yabo (hari benshi) bahinyuye (intumwa); nk’abantu ba Nuhu, aba Adi ndetse na Farawo wari ufite inyubako zitangaje"
  38,13,"N’aba Thamudu, abantu ba Lutwi ndetse n’aba Ayikat (b’i Mediyani), bose bari udutsiko"
  38,14,"Nta na kamwe muri two katahinyuye intumwa, nuko ibihano byanjye biba impamo"
  38,15,Aba nta kindi bategereje kitari urusaku rumwe rudasubira
  38,16,"Kandi baravuga bati \"Nyagasani wacu! Twihutishirize ibyo watugeneye (ibihano) mbere y’uko umunsi w’ibarura ugera"
  38,17,"Ihanganire ibyo bavuga (yewe Muhamadi), kandi wibuke umugaragu wacu Dawudi wari umunyembaraga (mu kutugaragira). Mu by’ukuri, yicuzaga kuri Allah cyane"
  38,18,"Mu by’ukuri, twashoboje imisozi gufatanya nawe (Dawudi) kudusingiza buri uko bucyeye n’uko bwije"
  38,19,"Ndetse n’inyoni zikusanyirijwe hamwe, zaramwumviye (zifatanya nawe mu kudusingiza)"
  38,20,"Maze dukomeza ubwami bwe, tunamuha ubushishozi no guca imanza neza"